{{catmain|Bella Coola Valley}}

The Bella Coola Valley is a region in the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], formed of a string of communities along [[British Columbia provincial highway 20]] from the western foot of its route over [[Heckman Pass]], and flanking the [[Bella Coola River]].

